---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Cleaning Checklist | CamCleans";
const description =
  "Typical cleaning tasks included in professional cleaning services across the United Kingdom.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/cleaning-checklist">

<section class="section">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Guide</span>
<h2>Typical cleaning checklist</h2>
<p>
Professional cleaning services follow structured task lists to ensure each property is cleaned consistently and thoroughly.
</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">

<div class="card">
<h3>Kitchen</h3>
<p>
Worktops cleaned, cupboard doors wiped, sink cleaned and appliances wiped externally.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Bathrooms</h3>
<p>
Toilets cleaned, sinks sanitised, tiles wiped and mirrors polished.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Living areas</h3>
<p>
Dusting surfaces, vacuuming carpets and wiping accessible fixtures.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Bedrooms</h3>
<p>
Dusting furniture, vacuuming floors and wiping surfaces.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Floors</h3>
<p>
Vacuuming carpets and mopping hard floors depending on the surface type.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>General surfaces</h3>
<p>
Light switches, handles and accessible surfaces wiped as part of the service.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="section section-tight">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Services</span>
<h2>Cleaning services that use this checklist</h2>
<p>
Different cleaning services apply these tasks in different levels of detail depending on the job type.
</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">

<div class="card">
<h3>End of tenancy cleaning</h3>
<p>
Detailed cleaning designed to prepare a property for landlord inspection.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Deep cleaning</h3>
<p>
More intensive cleaning for properties or homes needing a full reset.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>After builders cleaning</h3>
<p>
Removal of dust and debris after building or renovation work.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>

</Layout>